  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd6\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dba\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 27900 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "In June, 27900 people go to work in the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Only in June of this year, 27937 people have gone abroad for work, of which 18083 people have gone abroad on their own. In June, 9854 people went abroad for work through licensed foreign employment agencies.",
        "The total number of people who have gone abroad for work from January to the first week of July this year is 156179. 100,767 people have gone abroad by themselves and 55,411 people have gone abroad through licensed foreign employment agencies.",
        "From January to date, the highest number of people have gone abroad for work, and the number is 39216. 36229 have left for Qatar, 26098 for Saudi Arabia, 3219 for South Korea and 2576 for Japan.",
        "Also, from January to date, 46992 people have gone abroad for professional jobs and 49923 people have gone abroad for general professional jobs, and 38871 people have gone abroad for domestic jobs."
      ],
